<li id="cite_note-AEP-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-AEP_9-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Paul H. Rubin and C. Monica Capra. The evolutionary psychology of economics. In <span class="citation Journal">Roberts, S. C. (2011). <i>Applied Evolutionary Psychology</i>. Oxford University Press. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1093/acprof:oso/9780199586073.001.0001">10.1093/acprof:oso/9780199586073.001.0001</a>. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/9780199586073" title="Special:BookSources/9780199586073">9780199586073</a>.</span> <span class="plainlinks noprint" style="font-size:smaller"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Template_Cite_doi_10.1093.2Facprof_oso.2F9780199586073.001.0001&action=edit&editintro=Template_Cite_doi_editintro2.php.html">edit</a></span></span></li>
</ol>
